    "concept_sort_game": "esalemi concept sort game interface mpo na categorization practice. Benda items na kati sembo category buckets na demonstrate understanding of kelasiification concepts. Ngaimmediate feedzonga lakisas sembo pe insembo placements. Supports 2-4 categories pe any motángo of sortable items. Ya malamu mingi mpo na vocabulaire tiers, science kelasiifications, na grammar sorting.",
