    "persona_panel": "ANgai Persona chat panel - engage in ausimatic conversations na historical figures, scientists, literary characters, na custom personas. Salelás advanced ANgai na simulate period-accurate speech patterns, ktewledge, pe perspectives. Ya kokoka mpo na primary source analyse, perspective-taking, pe empathy-building exercises. Supports mulconseille response modes: Ngain-Character (fully immersive), Educational (with learning scaffya kalas), na Mixed (balanced approach).",
    "persona_card": "An ANgai persona tangay mpo na conversation. Each card lakisas character's nkombo, ntango period, pe expertise area. Tinda mpo na banda an interview - ANgai will respond ausimatically based on their historical conmakomi, beliefs, pe ktewledge. Salelá personas mpo na primary source analyse, perspective-taking exercises, na creative writing inspiration.",
    "persona_generate_button": "Salisá ANgai personas automatically uta na na yo source content. system analyzes na yo makomi na identify key figures, historical periods, na character archetypes pe salisás ausimatic conversational partners. Salisád personas include accurate biographical details, period-appropriate vocabulaire, pe conmakomiual ktewledge limitations (they won't ktew about events nsima ya their ntango).",
    "persona_select_button": "Pona this persona na banda na yo interview na conversation. Once ponaed, yo'll enter an immersive chat interface where yo can ask motunas, explore their perspective, pe earn XP mpo na meaningful exchanges. ANgai responds based on character's historical ktewledge, personality, pe cultural conmakomi.",
    "persona_back_btn": "Return na persona ponaion screen na pona a different character. Na yo current conversation progrès is automatically bommabe, pe yo can return na kobá it later. This allows exploring mulconseille perspectives on same historical motó.",
    "persona_custom_instructions": "Bakisá specific requirements mpo na how persona should behave during conversations. Examples: focus on a specific ntango period, emphasize certain beliefs na values, maintain particular speech patterns, na limit responses na historically accurate ktewledge. Molakisis can salelá this na align personas na specific learning objectives.",
    "persona_response_mode": "Pona how persona responds na salisá different learning experiences. NgaiN CHARACTER: Fully immersive historical mongongo na te modern explanations. EDUCATNgaiONAL: Character lobas kasi includes learning scaffya kalas, vocabulaire support, pe conmakomi. MNgaiXED: Balanced approach na ausimatic mongongo plus occasional clarifications. Pona based on moyekoli tangainess pe learning eyongás.",
    "persona_free_response": "Type na yo own fungola-ended response instead of ponaing uta na pre-written ba-options. Free response mode promotes creative expression, critical thinking, pe ausimatic dialogue skills. Responses are analyzed mpo na historical accuracy, empathy, pe depth of inquiry. Higher-quality motunas earn more XP.",
    "persona_hints_toggle": "Lakisa na bomba response suggestions pe conversation mokates. When fungolad, system provides scaffya kalaed motuna bandaers, historical conmakomi prompts, pe engagement suggestions. Lisalisiful mpo na moyekolis ya sika na historical inquiry na those esengelamiing support na fungola-ended motunaing. Molakisis can pekisa mokates mpo na more advanced assessment scenarios.",
    "persona_show_hints": "Disbandisa lisalisiful mokates mpo na engaging na persona. Mokates include historically relevant motunas na ask, motós character would zwa interesting, pe prompts that lead na deeper understanding. Ya malamu mingi mpo na moyekolis who esengelami scaffya kalaing na aren't sure how na banda a historical interview.",
    "persona_submit_btn": "Tinda na yo sango na persona character. Na yo motuna na response is analyzed mpo na relevance pe depth. ANgai persona will respond ausimatically based on their historical conmakomi, ktewledge, pe personality. Bisoll-crafted motunas that lakisa historical understanding earn bonus XP.",
    "persona_close": "Kanga persona conversation panel. Na yo chat historique pe earned XP are automatically bommabe. Yo can kobá this conversation later uta na Historique tab.",
    "persona_close_title": "Kanga Persona Chat",
    "persona_reflection_input": "Komá na yo reflection on conversation mpo na assessment. Reflect on what yo learned about historical figure, how their perspective differs uta na modern viewba-points, pe how this conversation changed na yo understanding. Reflections are evaluated using a rubric aligned na historical thinking skills pe can earn significant XP.",
    "persona_conclude": "End conversation pe salisá a comprehensive summary of na yo discussion. summary includes: key motós covered, historical insights gained, quality of na yo motunas, empathy demonstrated, pe XP earned. This summary can be exportered mpo na assessment, bakisáed na moyekoli portfolios, na salelád as a writing prompt mpo na reflection ba-activités.",
    "persona_save_chat": "Bomba this conversation na review na share later. Bommabe chats preserve sukisa dialogue, XP earned, ntangostamps, pe any reflections. Salelá bommabe chats mpo na moyekoli portfolios, assessment evidence, kelasi discussions, na exemplar models. Bommabe conversations can be exportered as PDF na shared na other moyekolis.",
    "persona_topic_spark": "Zwa a conversation bandaer na motó suggestion when yo're tet sure what na ask. system salisás historically relevant motunas based on persona's zongaground, expertise, pe ntango period. Ya malamu mingi mpo na overcoming komár's block na discovering ya sika angles na explore in na yo historical inquiry.",
    "persona_auto_send": "Automatically tinda na yo sango when yo telemisa typing mpo na a few secondes. Salisás a more natural conversational flow, especially when using mongongo dictation. Pekisa this if yo prefer na review pe bongisa sangos liboso ya tindaing, na if yo esengelami more ntango na compose thoughtful responses.",
    "analysis_generate_button": "Analyze na yo makomi ya source mpo na niveau ya kotanga, complexity, pe fonctionnalités.",
    "analysis_check_accuracy": "Fact-tala source content against reliable references.",
    "outline_generate_button": "Salisá a visual organizer uta na na yo source content.",
    "timeline_generate_button": "Salisá a ntangoline of events uta na na yo source content.",
    "timeline_topic": "main motó na thème of ntangoline being salisád. ANgai salisás historically accurate events based on this motó pe na yo source content. Example motós: American Revolution, Life Cycle of Stars, Shakespeare's Career. Events are automatically ordered chrotelogically mpo na sequencing practice.",
    "timeline_count": "Motángo of events na include in ntangoline. More events salisá longer, more detailed ntangolines kasi increase mpasi. Recommended: 4-6 events mpo na bandaners, 8-10 mpo na inlilobaediate, 12+ mpo na advanced learners. Events are bendagable mpo na sequencing practice nsima ya generation.",
    "faq_custom_instructions": "Bakisá specific requirements mpo na FAQ motunas (ndakisa, 'Focus on misconceptions').",
    "faq_count": "Motángo of FAQ motuna-eyate pairs na salisá.",
    "lesson_plan_custom_additions": "Bakisá specific ba-activités, standards, na content na include in plan ya lisolo.",
