    "group_create_button": "Salisá a ya sika moyekoli etuluku na entered nkombo.",
    "group_roster_list": "List of moyekolis in ponaed etuluku.",
    "roster_panel_header": "Kelasi Roster Key is na yo differentiation commpe center. Salisá moyekoli etulukus na unique learning profichiers (niveau ya kelasi, lokota, niveau ya kotanga, interests, DOK), sima salelá those profichiers na any generator. Roster données is stored in na yo browser's local storage pe never leaves na yo device unless yo explicitly exporter na sync na a live session. Salelá 'Salelá na Generator' na instantly configure paramètres mpo na a etuluku, na 'Differentiate by Etuluku' na batch-salisá ressources mpo na all etulukus at once.",
    "roster_import_export": "Ngaimporter a oyo elekily exportered roster JSON fichier, na exporter na yo current roster mpo na zongaup na sharing kati ya devices. Exportered fichiers contain etuluku nkombos, langis, moyekoli devoirs, pe all profichier paramètres.",
    "roster_sync_session": "Push na yo roster etuluku metadonnées na esalemi Firebase session so moyekolis are automatically assigned na their designated etuluku when they join. Etuluku-specific paramètres (TTS vitesse, karaoke mode) take effect on moyekoli devices.",
    "roster_batch_generate": "Salisá differentiated ressources mpo na every etuluku simultaneously. Pona which ressource types na salisá (adapted makomi, glossaire, quiz, mpe bisusu) pe system will iterate through each etuluku, saleláing their profichier paramètres liboso ya generating. Ressources are tagged na etuluku identifiers mpo na pete filtering.",
    "bridge_send_button": "Fungola Bridge Mode na tinda bilingual sangos na moyekolis during live instruction. Type a concept, etindamience, na instructions, pona a mode (Explain, Bongola, na Visual+Explain), pe pona a tarzwa etuluku. sango is salisád using ANgai na etuluku's lokota pe niveau ya kotanga paramètres, sima disbandisaed as a monene, tangaable bilingual panel on moyekoli devices na TTS pe karaoke highpɛing.",
